    <h3 class="text-center mb-5">Total Feedback: <span class="text-info"><%= total %></span></h3>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <!-- ðŸ“ Left Half -->
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3 class="text-light">Why Feedback Matters ðŸ’¬</h3>
        <p class="lead text-light mt-3">
          Feedback is the cornerstone of growth and progress. Whether it praises or points out areas to improve, 
          your input helps us evolve and provide a better experience. Every voice counts â€” and yours makes a difference. 
          Thank you for helping us shape a better tomorrow! ðŸŒŸ
        </p>

        <div class="mt-4">
